{
  "stem": "16163.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he could have tried to get my grandmother out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's the way I feel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Benno Silverberg, Benno, B-E-N-N-O, Benno Silverberg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Guy Stern, and he became a very famous man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's a professor in [INAUDIBLE] university, and we are very close.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I can really think of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened is that we were the last Jews left in Vlotho, because the other transports went already, and they took most of the people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was actually my mother, my father, my grandmother, and the family Haineman, which I mentioned before, which were two people over in their 80s.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My grandmother was in her 80s.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'd all-- Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Moshaim, I was talking about, he was in his 80s.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother, and father, and-- and me, we were the young ones.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that was the last transport out of Vlotho.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they came with trucks, and SS, and police, et cetera, and put us on the wagons, on the trucks, and took us to Bielefeld.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in Bielefeld was the next big town to us, they had the-- what was called the [GERMAN], you know, like where they collect-- a collection of people center.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they took us to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was-- I looked up in the papers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I thought it was July 1, '42.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was August 1, '42.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That we arrived in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A-- a friend of my father's came from Czechoslovakia for one reason or the other in Czechoslovakia, but he was not Jewish, a non-Jew.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Any he came-- called my-- had left a note for my father-- we didn't even have a telephone at the time or anything-- to come to his office.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
